msgctxt "dn3:42.1"
msgid ""
"“Iti kho, ambaṭṭha, itthiyā vā itthiṃ karitvā purisena vā purisaṃ karitvā "
"khattiyāva seṭṭhā, hīnā brāhmaṇā."
msgstr ""
"“And so, Ambaṭṭha, the aristocrats are superior and the brahmins inferior, "
"whether comparing women with women or men with men."

msgctxt "dn3:42.2"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, idha brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇaṃ kismiñcideva pakaraṇe "
"khuramuṇḍaṃ karitvā bhassapuṭena vadhitvā raṭṭhā vā nagarā vā pabbājeyyuṃ."
msgstr ""
